-- Pamplona buys UK firm Beacon Rail for around $450 mln 
-- By Freya Berry
-- Tue May 06, 2014 03:12AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, May 6 (Reuters) - Investment manager Pamplona Capital Management is to buy UK train leasing company Beacon Rail for around $450 million from a subsidiary of Japan's Mitsubishi UFJ Financial Group <8306.T>.

